text: Andrei Igorevich Svechnikov is a Russian professional ice hockey winger currently playing for the Carolina Hurricanes of the National Hockey League. He was projected as a top pick in the 2018 NHL Entry Draft, where he was drafted second overall by the Hurricanes.
